metadata.name: Lamborghini #1
metadata.description: A Lamborghini NFT is a unique, one-of-a-kind digital asset that represents ownership of a virtual Lamborghini car. The asset is stored on a blockchain and can be bought, sold, and traded like any other cryptocurrency. The NFT is verified and authenticated by the blockchain, making it a secure and verifiable way for enthusiasts to own a piece of the Lamborghini brand.
